  "description": "This individual is a reanimated human corpse, defined by zombie_green skinTone stretched tight over prominent bone and a rigid, uneven gait. Gray eyes sit deep beneath a collapsed brow ridge, giving the face a fixed, hollow vigilance. Black hair remains in sparse, matted clumps, exposing lesions along the scalp and a torn left ear. The jawline is visibly misaligned from an old fracture that never properly set, producing a permanent slackness to the mouth.",
